thy-and-dulquer-s-performances-81024|title=After watching mahanati Rajamouli raves about keerthy and dulquers performances|last=|first=|date=10 May 2018|website=www.thenewsminute.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728062401/https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/after-watching-mahanati-rajamouli-raves-about-keerthy-and-dulquer-s-performances-81024|archive-date=28 July 2019|url-status=live|access-date=28 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Nadigaiyar Thilagam]]''\n|Tamil\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/review/2018/may/12/nadigaiyar-thilagam-movie-review-a-well-made-biopic-thats-in-love-with-its-subject-1813416.html|title='Nadigaiyar Thilagam' movie review: A well-made biopic that's in love with its subject|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=28 July 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728062543/http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/review/2018/may/12/nadigaiyar-thilagam-movie-review-a-well-made-biopic-thats-in-love-with-its-subject-1813416.html|archive-date=28 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Karwaan (film)|Karwaan]]'' \n| Avinash Rajpurohit\n| Akaarsh Khurana\n| [[Hindi]]\n| Hindi Debut \n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news18.com/news/movies/karwaan-film-review-irrfan-khan-and-dulquer-salmaan-starrer-is-a-road-trip-worth-taking-1833741.html|title=Karwaan Film Review: Irrfan Khan and Dulquer Salmaan-Starrer Is a Road Trip Worth Taking|website=News18|access-date=28 July 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728062734/https://www.news18.com/news/movies/karwaan-film-review-irrfan-khan-and-dulquer-salmaan-starrer-is-a-road-trip-worth-taking-1833741.html|archive-date=28 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/entertainment/karwaan-is-the-perfect-bollywood-debut-for-dulquer-salmaan-film-proves-the-actor-is-best-of-his-generation-4912331.html|title=Karwaan is the perfect Bollywood debut for Dulquer Salmaan; film proves the actor is