 Kavya Madhavan bag Asiavision awards|work=[[Emirates 24/7]]|author=VM Sathish|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060116/http://www.emirates247.com/entertainment/mammotty-kavya-madhavan-bag-asiavision-awards-2013-11-05-1.526962|archivedate=4 March 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n\n|-\n|rowspan=9|2013\n|[[Asianet Film Awards]] \n| rowspan=2|Best New Face(Male)\n|<ref name=\"Retrosp\" />\n|-\n|Rowspan =2|[[Vanitha Film Awards]] \n|<ref name=\"Retrosp\" />\n|-\n|Best Star pair\n|''[[Ustad Hotel]]''\n| {{cn|date=December 2019}}\n|-\n|Amrita TV awards\n| Best Debut (Male)\n|rowspan=2|''[[Second Show]]''\n|<ref name=\"Retrosp\" />\n|-\n|Jaihind Film awards\n| Best New Face(Male)\n|<ref name=\"Retrosp\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Filmfare Awards South|Filmfare Awards]]\n| [[Filmfare Award for Best Actor \u2013 Malayalam|Best Actor]]\n| ''[[Ustad Hotel]]''\n| {{Nom}}\n|<ref name=\"UHNom\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/filmfare-awards-2013-south-complete-list-of-nominees-487119|title=Filmfare Awards 2013 (South): Complete List of Nominees|publisher=International Business Times|date=6 July 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617174038/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/filmfare-awards-2013-south-complete-list-of-nominees-487119|archivedate=17 June 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Filmfare Award for Best Male Debut \u2013 South|Best Debut (Male)]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Second Show]]''\n| rowspan=7 {{Won}}\n|<ref name=\"r1ff\">{{cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/filmfare-awards-south-dhanush-eega-win-big-awards/408186-71-177.html|title=Filmfare Awards (South): The complete list of winners|work=[[CNN-IBN]]|date=21 July 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510051756/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/filmfare-awards-south-dhanush-eega-win-big-awards/408186-71-177.html|archivedate=10 May 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2nd South Indian International Movie Awards|South Indian International Movie Awards]]\n| Best Debut (Male)\n|<ref name=\"Retrosp\" />\n|-\n| Asiavision Awards\n| Per