ai Moodi Pesavum]]''\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/vijay-awards-2015-complete-list-of-winners-news-tamil-pe0nhUfhdeigd.html|title=Vijay Awards 2015 \u2013 Complete list of winners|publisher=Sify|date=26 April 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624074413/http://www.sify.com/movies/vijay-awards-2015-complete-list-of-winners-news-tamil-pe0nhUfhdeigd.html|archivedate=24 June 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| Vikatan Awards\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/vikatan-awards-2014-dhanush-dulquer-salmaan-sathuranga-vettai-honoured-winners-list-619905|title=Vikatan Awards 2014: Dhanush, Dulquer Salmaan, 'Sathuranga Vettai' Honoured|publisher=International Business Times|date=9 January 2015|author=Nicy V.P|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011752/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/vikatan-awards-2014-dhanush-dulquer-salmaan-sathuranga-vettai-honoured-winners-list-619905|archivedate=5 March 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\"| 2016\n|[[Asianet Film Awards]] \n| Most popular actor \n| rowspan=\"6\" | ''[[Charlie (2015 Malayalam film)|Charlie]]''\n|<ref name=\"Retrosp\" />\n|-\n| Filmfare Awards\n| Best Actor\n \n| {{Nom}}\n|<ref name=\"Filmfare actor\" />\n|-\n| [[Kerala State Film Award]]\n| [[Kerala State Film Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| rowspan=2 {{Won}}\n|<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| NAFA Awards\n| rowspan=2| Best Actor\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Dulquer Salmaan-Parvathy's 'Charlie' sweeps first edition of North American Film Award (NAFA) 2016 in US|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/dulquer-salmaan-parvathys-charlie-sweeps-first-edition-north-american-film-award-nafa-2016-687140|date=19 July 2016|publisher=International Business Times|author=Anu James|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720182030/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/dulquer-salmaan-parvathys-charlie-sweeps-first-edition-north-american-film-award-nafa-2016-687140|archivedate=20 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[5th South Indian International Movie Awards|South Indian Interna